<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Setup</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>$5</li>
                <li>Create creature deck</li>
                <li><b>Heroes</b> add heroes and new creatures to deck</li>
                <li><b>Divine Favors</b> include Priestess, Magic Item, Divine Favors</li>
                <li><b>Divine Artifacts</b> shuffle 5 artifact cards into creature deck</li>
                <li><b>Titans map</b> randomly place 1 of each building; include Kronos board</li>
                <li><b>Special Metro</b> draw 2, return other 3 to box</li>
                <li><b>Monuments</b> draw N, return rest to box. display all</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Free Positioning</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>$7</li>
                <li>No units on board</li>
                <li>Round 0: auction, limit 1 player on Apollo</li>
                <li>Round 1: clear Gods and shuffle, skip income phase</li>
                <li>In order, place 2 troops and 2 fleets
                    <ul>
                        <li>troops on 2 different islands (adjacent territories on Titans map)</li>
                        <li>fleets in 2 different spaces, adjacent to island(s) they control</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Bonus for each God
                    <ul>
                        <li>Poseidon: +1 fleet; may use 3rd space on base map</li>
                        <li>Ares: +1 troop; may choose 3rd island on base map</li>
                        <li>Athena: +1 philosopher</li>
                        <li>Zeus: +1 priest</li>
                        <li>Apollo: +1 prosperity marker (also +$1 on Titans map)</li>
                        <li>Kronos: +1 titan; +1 titan or +1 building</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Creature Row</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Generally: discard $2 creature, slide, fill spaces</li>
                <li>Round 1: 1 creature in $4 space</li>
                <li>Round 2: slide & draw so $2 space is empty but others are not</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>End Game</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Check for 2 metropolises at <i>end</i> of round</li>
                <li>Ties: most metropolises, then most gold</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Round Order</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Update Creature row</li>
                <li>Roll Hades dice, Arrange God tiles</li>
                <li>Revenue, Hero upkeep</li>
                <li>Auction</li>
                <li>Actions</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>Combat</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Roll and add number of troops/fleets</li>
                <li>Add 1 for forts and defender's ports</li>
                <li>Loser removes a troop/fleet; both remove for a tie</li>
                <li>Defender can retreat</li>
                <li>Attacker can retreat</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

